    <h3 class="mb-2">Simplicity</h3>
    <p class="leading-6 text-gray-700">Kindmetrics is kind to you as to the visitors. It is simple to setup, just need to add a codesnippet and you are up and running in no-time. The dashboard is built to be simple to use with everything on one page.</p>
