    <p class="leading-6 text-gray-700">We save no cookies on your visitors computers and we don't save personal information. We don't use CDN's or third party to get countries or anything for you, we do all that ourselves, meaning the data is not seen by anyone else but you and us. Read more about our <a href="/data-privacy/">data privacy here</a>.</p>
